    "It does so based on error severity (e.g., core errors that impact comprehension are prioritized over stylistic suggestions) and a Markov chain prediction of the learner's past errors.",
    "This approach ensures that teaching interventions are both precise and progressive.",
    "Together, these mechanisms form a \"white-box\" feedback system, ensuring that the AI decision-making process is transparent and meets the auditability requirements of educational settings.",
    "The system also includes a module for analyzing argumentation logic.",
    "Argument structure is identified using a fine-tuned BERT model that detects theses, premises, and conclusions, enabling the construction of paragraph-level logical maps."
